text: Adoram Keisi (; born June 17, 1972) is a retired Israeli professional football player. He was a left back. == Honours == * Israeli Premier League: 2000–01, 2001–02, 2003–04, 2004–05, 2005–06 * Israeli State Cup: 1997–98 * Toto Cup: 2002–03, 2005–06 == References == * אדורם קייסי at Maccabi Haifa FC Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Israeli footballers Category:Jewish Israeli sportspeople
